net.dean.jraw.http

Class HttpRequest.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dean.jraw.http.HttpRequest.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    HttpRequest

    public static final class HttpRequest.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides an interface to create objects that model HTTP requests. Borrowed heavily from OkHttp's Request.Builder class.
